response.overview: Rausch und/and Craziness was a 2-day joint concert by Roselia and RAISE A SUILEN.  Additional performance for Rausch was held on February 1, 2020 at Musashino Forest Sports Plaza, Chofu, Tokyo  The Blu-rays for the additional performances were included in the limited editions of Roselia's 11th single and of RAISE A SUILEN's 6th single. Roselia's single was released on January 20, 2021 while RAISE A SUILEN's single was released on January 27, 2021.
response.title: Roselia - Rausch
